- [ ] **Error Prevention**: Guards against common user mistakes
- [ ] **Recovery**: Easy paths to correct errors or go back
- [ ] **Efficiency**: Shortcuts for power users, defaults for new users
- [ ] **Accessibility**: Keyboard navigation and screen reader support
- [ ] **Performance**: Interactions feel responsive (<100ms feedback)

### 5.3 Â· Handoff Quality Checklist
- [ ] **Specifications**: Complete measurements, colors, and typography
