- [ ] **Responsive**: Behavior defined for all target breakpoints  
- [ ] **Edge Cases**: Loading, empty, and error states designed
- [ ] **Documentation**: Clear annotations and usage guidelines
- [ ] **Developer Review**: Technical feasibility confirmed

